                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I havent tried the trials without a snarer, my boyfriend is a druid and we generally do them together. 
<br />
I've done tons of tipt trials and with over 8khps and 500+ aa's I cant see someone waiting for hasted pet to hit before they cast WoM.  Pookas maybe but the proc'ing pets, I'd have to see to believe. <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />
